snippet.title: Ailuri Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
🌱 Wishlist:  http://tinyurl.com/AiluriSteam

🌱 Kickstarter: http://tinyurl.com/ailuriurl

Our first Kickstarter Trailer for our game, Ailuri. 

Ailuri is a 2D, level based platformer with hand drawn art and detailed levels. Rescue other endangered animals in this fantastical adventure!
